title: #92Noon! Osborn/Burns/Florio/Rashad/Gleeman/Chavous
description: Full Tuesday! Meet Vikings rookie receiver KJ Osborn, a Gophers catchup with Ryan Burns, Florio finishes the first hour....tremendous interview with Vikings great Ahmad Rashad ends the middle hour, then it's Aaron Gleeman, shutdown shoutouts and Corey Chavous with a draft recap to end 92Noon!
